#

Saffron-infused Butternut Squash Ravioli

$25
600 kcal
Difficulty: 80%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

DairyEggsWheat

Dietary Tags:

Vegetarian

Tags:

GourmetComfort FoodPasta

Description

Delicate homemade ravioli filled with a rich saffron butternut squash mixture, complemented by a nutty brown butter sage sauce.

Ingredients

  • Butternut Squash: 1 medium, peeled and cubed
  • Saffron Threads: a pinch
  • Ricotta Cheese: 1/2 cup
  • Parmesan Cheese: 1/4 cup, grated
  • All-Purpose Flour: 2 cups
  • Eggs: 3 large
  • Butter: 1/2 cup
  • Fresh Sage Leaves: 10-12 leaves
  • Salt: to taste
  • Black Pepper: to taste
  • Nutmeg: 1/4 teaspoon, freshly grated
  • Olive Oil: 1 tablespoon
